source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000010_GILGAMESH<tab>To my side, Enkidu! The battle is joined!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000010_GILGAMESH<tab>行くぞ、エンキドウ……我が友よ！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000020_GILGAMESH<tab>Owww! It hurts! It hurts!Enkidu! Your master wants for succor!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000020_GILGAMESH<tab>やるじゃねぇか……エンキドウ、手当を頼むぜ！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000030_GILGAMESH<tab>Fancy some feathers...bird brain?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000030_GILGAMESH<tab>鶏になっちまえ！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000040_GILGAMESH<tab>This should cut you down to size...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000040_GILGAMESH<tab>人形と遊んでな！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000050_GILGAMESH<tab>Fight on, Enkidu, my ever faithful─hm!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000050_GILGAMESH<tab>エンキドウ！　後はお前に任せたぜ！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000060_GILGAMESH<tab>Enkidu! Are the bonds of our friendship so fragile!?
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000060_GILGAMESH<tab>ありゃ……エンキドウ……？
置いてけぼりは、なしだぜー！？
これが本当、本気の……最後の戦いだぜ！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000070_GILGAMESH<tab>Not the <var 1A 02 /var>strongest<var 1A 01 /var> of swords, but it should suffice.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000070_GILGAMESH<tab>くらえ、マサムネ！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000080_GILGAMESH<tab>Gilgamesh is in the mood...for dancing!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000080_GILGAMESH<tab>剣の舞い！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000090_GILGAMESH<tab>Divide and conquer, Gilgamesh style!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000090_GILGAMESH<tab>秘技…我流雪月花！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000100_GILGAMESH<tab>...And now for something truly <var 1A 02 /var>shocking<var 1A 01 /var>!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000100_GILGAMESH<tab>うりゃっ、電撃！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000110_GILGAMESH<tab>What's the matter, friend? All tied up?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000110_GILGAMESH<tab>そぉれ、大捕物！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000120_GILGAMESH<tab>Uh-oh! Someone just woke the dragon...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000120_GILGAMESH<tab>いでよ、雲蒸竜変！

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000130_GILGAMESH<tab>You have some skill, I'll give you that...
But Gilgamesh has only just begun to fight!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000130_GILGAMESH<tab>なかなかやるじゃねぇか！
だが……オレたちの戦いは、まだ始まったばかりだ！

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000140_GILGAMESH<tab>Most impressive!
Very well─I, too, shall fight with all my strength!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000140_GILGAMESH<tab>じ、上等だ……よぉし！
ここからは、お互い出し惜しみはナシだぜ！？

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000150_GILGAMESH<tab>No! The mighty Gilgamesh will not be defeated!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000150_GILGAMESH<tab>まだだ……まだ、戦いは終わっちゃいねぇ！！

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100010_GILGAMESH<tab>At long last, we meet again on the battlefield!
I daresay Enkidu shall come to enjoy our tussles as much as I.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100010_GILGAMESH<tab>Wie schön, dass du meiner Einladung gefolgt bist!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100020_GILGAMESH<tab><var 1A 02 /var>You<var 1A 01 /var>, however, might not find this one so enjoyable.
...Unless you enjoy getting pounded senseless. Hah!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100020_GILGAMESH<tab>Hier können Enkidu und ich uns richtig austoben!
Dir werden die Ohren schlackern!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200010_GILGAMESH<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Me<var 1A 01 /var>? Run away? Hah! I-I was but seeking out a
more suitable spot to celebrate my inevitable victory!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200010_GILGAMESH<tab>Dachtest du etwa, ich wollte fliehen?
Hab nur ein gemütlicheres Plätzchen gesucht!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200020_GILGAMESH<tab>But enough exposition! Now we fight like men!
And ladies! And ladies who dress like men!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200020_GILGAMESH<tab>Ich werde dir zeigen, was in mir steckt!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200030_GILGAMESH<tab>For Gilgamesh...it is transmogrifying time!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200030_GILGAMESH<tab>Gilgamesch-Metamorphooose!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200040_GILGAMESH<tab>The mightiest warrior ever to grace Eorzea stands before you─
by which I mean <var 1A 02 /var>I<var 1A 01 /var>, Gilgamesh! Prepare yourself!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200040_GILGAMESH<tab>Ich bin Gilgamesch, der stärkste Schwertkämpfer Eorzeas!
Möge der Kampf beginnen!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300010_GILGAMESH<tab>To think that my full complement of arms would avail me naught...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300010_GILGAMESH<tab>Selbst mit acht Armen bin ich dir nicht gewachsen.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300020_GILGAMESH<tab>No more high jinks from Gilgamesh. You have my word.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300020_GILGAMESH<tab>Also gut, ich gebe auf. Du hast mich überzeugt.

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300030_GILGAMESH<tab>The Treaty-Blade, too, I shall return.
...Just as soon as I remember where I hid it.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300030_GILGAMESH<tab>Das Schwert des Paktes geb ich euch auch zurück.
Ich habe es vor den Ruinen im Wald versteckt.

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300040_GILGAMESH<tab>Anyway, I yield to your unparalleled puissance!
Spare my insignificant life, I beg of you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300040_GILGAMESH<tab>Bitte, verschone mich. Ich flehe dich an!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400010_GILGAMESH<tab>...NOT! Ha, I lied...again! Like a rug! Oh, I kill me!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400010_GILGAMESH<tab>Als würde ich jemals aufgeben!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400020_GILGAMESH<tab>You can take that fusty old blade for all I care! I thirst for <var 1A 02 /var>true<var 1A 01 /var>
power, and naught save the strongest of swords will suffice!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400020_GILGAMESH<tab>Das olle Schwert ist mir doch völlig egal!
Nur die stärksten Waffen sind gut genug für Gilgamesch!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400030_GILGAMESH<tab>Warrior of Light─you have proven a worthy opponent.
But I warn you─treasure every moment with your weapon.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400030_GILGAMESH<tab>Immerhin habe ich einen würdigen Gegner gefunden!
Ich freue mich schon auf unser nächstes Treffen!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400040_GILGAMESH<tab>For as sure as day follows night, the hour will come when
I claim it as mine own! Till we meet again!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400040_GILGAMESH<tab>Eines Tages schnapp ich mir auch deine Waffe!
Ach was, dein ganzes Arsenal!
